sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as DocumentOwner
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant DocCtrl as DocumentController
participant DocSvc as DocumentService
participant DocDb as MongoDocument
participant Webhook as WebhookService
User->>Client: Tao document metadata
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/documents
Gateway->>DocCtrl: createDocument
DocCtrl->>DocSvc: validate owner + payload
DocSvc->>DocDb: insert document currentVersion
DocSvc->>Webhook: send document.created
DocSvc-->>Client: 201
User->>Client: Upload version moi
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/documents/:id/versions
Gateway->>DocCtrl: uploadNewVersion
DocSvc->>DocDb: push current -> previousVersions
DocSvc->>DocDb: set new currentVersion
alt Owner hop le
  DocSvc-->>Client: 200 updated
else Forbidden/Not found
  DocSvc-->>Client: 403/404
end
User->>Client: Xoa document
Client->>Gateway: DELETE /api/documents/:id
DocSvc->>DocDb: set isActive=false
